        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">01</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <h3>Create a board</h3>
            <p>Set the stage — give your world a name, a genre, and a set of house rules. Invite your co-authors.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-line"></div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">02</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <h3>Write your character</h3>
            <p>Fill out a character sheet or start bare-bones. The page is blank — begin wherever you like.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-line"></div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">03</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <h3>Post and play</h3>
            <p>React, reply, roll dice. The story grows one post at a time, at whatever pace suits your life.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

